item.title: Can't logg onto mopar server down ? plz tell me what to do
item.dc:creator: @Owned_Irl1 Owned Irl
item.description:
@Owned_Irl1 wrote:

when you go to the server advertisement section…

Find a server you want to play on…

For starters, try to find one that doesnt require Hamachi…

Use the information from the owner’s post, and apply it to the moparscape client…

For instance if the server was HiScape… and his Ip was hiscape.no-ip.org

then u type in that ip on your client… also make sure you have the right port for the server…

the common ports are 5555, and 43594 . To change the port to the correct one… go to your client… go to file… change port… and type it in…

also make sure the server is online…

If you got any more questions, send me a Pm…
